name: Governor Eric Holcomb
tweet: The plans enumerated a nearly 10:1 capitalization leverage ratio from private and public sources as compared to state investment.

name: Governor Eric Holcomb
tweet: Following the evaluation, the #READI review committee members proposed funding recommendations to the IEDC Board of Directors.  The plans included housing, trails, broadband, childcare & wellness initiatives, workforce development programs, & telling Indiana’s story to the world.

name: Governor Eric Holcomb
tweet: All 17 regions presented to the external review committee, allowing each region to present an overview of its plan to distill its vision, goals & strategies to positively impact the area’s quality of place, innovation, entrepreneurship, talent attraction & workforce development.

name: Governor Eric Holcomb
tweet: The #READI review committee, an external seven-member citizen committee, reviewed and scored the plans based on the established guidelines and against other relevant data, including historical population trends.

name: Governor Eric Holcomb
tweet: These plans will shape Indiana for generations to come and bring value to our state like nothing we’ve witnessed before. I want to thank the General Assembly for having the courage and leadership to prioritize this initiative.

name: Governor Eric Holcomb
tweet: The 17 regions submitted innovative, creative & visionary projects that will result in a positive economic impact on Indiana’s future. It took immense collaboration between communities as they put aside their own visions & worked together to present the best plan for the region.

name: Governor Eric Holcomb
tweet: The total requests tripled the allocated $500 million #READI budget, as submissions from the 17 regions amounted to more than $1.5 billion in demand and detailed nearly 800 projects and programs with a potential investment of $15.2 billion.
